{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/full-front-end-developer/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Traverse"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"dc521a67-dae0-5f61-8b39-1b4b21090e3a","excerpt":"零基礎掌握大前端的技能 什麼是大前端？ 雖然是個很常聽到的詞，但是看了一下網上的資料，其實也沒有定義的很明確 透過手邊的資料跟自己的理解 總結出大前端需要具備這幾個能力 首先是「JS…","html":"<h2 id=\"零基礎掌握大前端的技能\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%9B%B6%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%A4%A7%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD\" aria-label=\"零基礎掌握大前端的技能 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>零基礎掌握大前端的技能</h2>\n<p>什麼是大前端？</p>\n<p>雖然是個很常聽到的詞，但是看了一下網上的資料，其實也沒有定義的很明確<br>\n透過手邊的資料跟自己的理解<br>\n總結出大前端需要具備這幾個能力</p>\n<!-- more -->\n<p>首先是「JS編程能力」，這是身為前端開發都具備的能力<br>\n而設計知識基礎、重構能力和調教能力這三個方面是比較弱的部分</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 530px; margin: initial;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"skill set\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/traverse/static/b0f21052f537a5030407b23d472bef4f/d0861/skill-set.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/traverse/static/b0f21052f537a5030407b23d472bef4f/4ec73/skill-set.jpg 180w,\n/traverse/static/b0f21052f537a5030407b23d472bef4f/158ba/skill-set.jpg 360w,\n/traverse/static/b0f21052f537a5030407b23d472bef4f/d0861/skill-set.jpg 530w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>這篇文章主要著重在「設計」這個方向</p>\n<h2 id=\"設計規範\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E8%A6%8F%E7%AF%84\" aria-label=\"設計規範 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>設計規範</h2>\n<p>說到設計，在產品應用層面來說<br>\n就像開發有代碼的規範，設計也會有對應的設計規範，都是為了保證產出物的品質<br>\n一般來說設計團隊會根據經驗與項目，總結出來的一套屬於自己的設計規範<br>\n了解了下目前幾個比較廣為人之的設計規範，像是 Material Design, Ant Design…等</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; margin: initial;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.111111111111114%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"material design\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/traverse/static/c5d022b61a7541cbccef5b4d0b5adadb/37523/material-design.png\"\n        srcset=\"/traverse/static/c5d022b61a7541cbccef5b4d0b5adadb/e9ff0/material-design.png 180w,\n/traverse/static/c5d022b61a7541cbccef5b4d0b5adadb/f21e7/material-design.png 360w,\n/traverse/static/c5d022b61a7541cbccef5b4d0b5adadb/37523/material-design.png 720w,\n/traverse/static/c5d022b61a7541cbccef5b4d0b5adadb/302a4/material-design.png 1080w,\n/traverse/static/c5d022b61a7541cbccef5b4d0b5adadb/07a9c/material-design.png 1440w,\n/traverse/static/c5d022b61a7541cbccef5b4d0b5adadb/9dbdb/material-design.png 2622w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; margin: initial;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.44444444444444%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ant design\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/traverse/static/4e16f846d8bd265b2c9f9aa868c4570f/37523/ant-design.png\"\n        srcset=\"/traverse/static/4e16f846d8bd265b2c9f9aa868c4570f/e9ff0/ant-design.png 180w,\n/traverse/static/4e16f846d8bd265b2c9f9aa868c4570f/f21e7/ant-design.png 360w,\n/traverse/static/4e16f846d8bd265b2c9f9aa868c4570f/37523/ant-design.png 720w,\n/traverse/static/4e16f846d8bd265b2c9f9aa868c4570f/302a4/ant-design.png 1080w,\n/traverse/static/4e16f846d8bd265b2c9f9aa868c4570f/07a9c/ant-design.png 1440w,\n/traverse/static/4e16f846d8bd265b2c9f9aa868c4570f/f45e2/ant-design.png 2628w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>設計規範其中包含了這幾個方面</p>\n<ul>\n<li>配色：包含產品的主色調、控件顏色、狀態顏色…等等</li>\n<li>Layout：包含PC端與Mobile端的Layout</li>\n<li>字體：字型、字號、字色、以及行高</li>\n<li>Icon：對於比較多icon使用場景的業務，會規範 icon 的大小、各種狀態色值</li>\n<li>間距</li>\n<li>… 等等</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"設計輸出\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E8%BC%B8%E5%87%BA\" aria-label=\"設計輸出 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>設計輸出</h2>\n<p>有了一套設計規範後，設計團隊會根據設計規範輸出設計稿給到開發。<br>\n在開發過程中，第 一個遇到的狀況是「如何準確進行視覺還原？」<br>\n大部分的設計師使用的都是 PS 或 Sketch 來進行繪製設計稿</p>\n<p>而近期又以 Sketch 為流行使用，其中一個原因是一些插件把設計與開發溝通的橋樑串接起來</p>\n<p>像是以下兩個插件，可以將設計稿導出成瀏覽器可預覽的視覺</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Sketch Measure</li>\n<li>Zeplin</li>\n</ul>\n<p>但是這兩個插件的功能有稍微的不同，比較如下圖</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 569px; margin: initial;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Sketch measure vs Zeplin\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/traverse/static/0156987f1f3197638bcb94dc8552ad0e/854dc/sketch-measure-vs-zeplin.png\"\n        srcset=\"/traverse/static/0156987f1f3197638bcb94dc8552ad0e/e9ff0/sketch-measure-vs-zeplin.png 180w,\n/traverse/static/0156987f1f3197638bcb94dc8552ad0e/f21e7/sketch-measure-vs-zeplin.png 360w,\n/traverse/static/0156987f1f3197638bcb94dc8552ad0e/854dc/sketch-measure-vs-zeplin.png 569w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 569px) 100vw, 569px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Sketch Measure 和 Zeplin 最大的差異在於 Measure 只支援 Sketch，而且免費<br>\n既然已經有 Sketch Measure 或 Zeplin 這些 Plugins，為什麼還要學習 PS 以及 Sketch 的基本技巧？</p>\n<p>以下是以 Sketch Measure 為出發點做比較</p>\n<ul>\n<li>不支援導出 PNG 以外的格式，包含 SVG 等常用格式（必須使用 Sketch 內建的導出圖片功能）</li>\n<li>Sketch 是一個更新頻率很高的軟體，如果Plugin更新的速度跟不上，在 Sketch 更新之後可能會有些問題，導致無法正常使用</li>\n<li>設計師不一定使用 Sketch 做頁面設計</li>\n<li>據自己了解和過往經驗，在許多團隊中設計師只提供設計稿並不做切圖的動作，基本上的切圖與一些設計稿的操作是 UI 開發需要自行處理，因此我認為我們要往大前端的方向，基本的設計軟體操作技巧還是要掌握</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"視覺還原\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%A6%96%E8%A6%BA%E9%82%84%E5%8E%9F\" aria-label=\"視覺還原 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>視覺還原</h2>\n<p>有了以上的基本的設計知識，開始來說拿到設計原稿後如何進行實踐，第一步先進行設計拆解</p>\n<h3 id=\"設計拆解\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E6%8B%86%E8%A7%A3\" aria-label=\"設計拆解 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>設計拆解</h3>\n<p>主要有兩個步驟：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>設計拆解</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; margin: initial;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49.44444444444444%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"UI breakdown\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/traverse/static/fe1db893543437a0e4f67e25173c3772/80e3c/ui_breakdown.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/traverse/static/fe1db893543437a0e4f67e25173c3772/4ec73/ui_breakdown.jpg 180w,\n/traverse/static/fe1db893543437a0e4f67e25173c3772/158ba/ui_breakdown.jpg 360w,\n/traverse/static/fe1db893543437a0e4f67e25173c3772/80e3c/ui_breakdown.jpg 720w,\n/traverse/static/fe1db893543437a0e4f67e25173c3772/6a068/ui_breakdown.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>交互確認：了解設計師最終想要呈現的效果</li>\n</ol>\n<img src=\"/traverse/e8ffcea8b4567801c9be3be0813c79d8/ux-ensure.gif\" alt=\"UX ensure\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;\">\n<p>然後就可以開始對設計稿的圖片資源進行導出</p>\n<h3 id=\"圖片處理\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9C%96%E7%89%87%E8%99%95%E7%90%86\" aria-label=\"圖片處理 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>圖片處理</h3>\n<p>底下這張圖是我將 PS 與 Sketch 幾個常見的操作所做的整理</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; margin: initial;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.111111111111114%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ps-and-sketch\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/traverse/static/8e1a73a7770d357cad8c7ac737eb072c/80e3c/ps-and-sketch.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/traverse/static/8e1a73a7770d357cad8c7ac737eb072c/4ec73/ps-and-sketch.jpg 180w,\n/traverse/static/8e1a73a7770d357cad8c7ac737eb072c/158ba/ps-and-sketch.jpg 360w,\n/traverse/static/8e1a73a7770d357cad8c7ac737eb072c/80e3c/ps-and-sketch.jpg 720w,\n/traverse/static/8e1a73a7770d357cad8c7ac737eb072c/6a068/ps-and-sketch.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>詳細操作步驟可以參考 <a href=\"/traverse/d3d82a3b1936b8615c6ff1403d80b6ac/ps&sketch.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">PS 和 Sketch 詳細切圖操作步驟 <i class=\"fas fa-external-link-alt\"></i></a></p>\n<p>至於要導出什麼格式、以什麼方式實踐，如下述</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>圖片格式：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>jpg 格式 - banner或矩形圖片等顏色豐富，壓縮率高</li>\n<li>png 或 svg 格式 - 半透明，或需要適應不同背景的icon圖標</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>圖片壓縮：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>jpg 壓縮 - PS或Sketch中導出時壓縮到85%</li>\n<li>png 壓縮 - 推薦 <a href=\"https://tinypng.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">TinyPNG</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>圖片合併：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Sprite 雪碧圖</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>加 lazyload 懶加載，優化用戶等待體驗</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"圖片格式\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9C%96%E7%89%87%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F\" aria-label=\"圖片格式 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>圖片格式</h3>\n<h4 id=\"base64\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#base64\" aria-label=\"base64 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Base64</h4>\n<p>這類圖片從誕生起，基本上很少被更新。<br>\n適用場景：這類圖片的實際尺寸很小</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 29px; margin: initial;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"base64 icon\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/traverse/static/7a760edfb7432c7f60a6f660754bf86c/9a445/base64_icon.png\"\n        srcset=\"/traverse/static/7a760edfb7432c7f60a6f660754bf86c/9a445/base64_icon.png 29w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 29px) 100vw, 29px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">data</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>image/png<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>base64<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACcAAAAnCAMAAAC7faEHAAAAM1B\nMVEUAAAD///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////+3leKCAAAAEHRSTlMA3dKElohES/fBfT7n\ncFA4OSNapAAAAHxJREFUOMvt0MsKgCAUBuFjlt3L93/aFiUjCL9Iq6BZf6uxIWu3u6HosJjVPS4W9Q3OhdT5uJA3J9eZ\nykdchc04xfyIU8xwkuEkw2mG0wwnmHQw6WDSwbSDaQfTDqbdAssq3TrBCAdcTDr6mAvOee34/LvXbnKVttvVa3A\nXnU0WqafEyB4AAAAASUVORK5CYII=<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> no-repeat<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>優點</th>\n<th>缺點</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>減少了HTTP請求</td>\n<td>IE 6/7 瀏覽器不支持</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>某些文件可以避免跨域的問題</td>\n<td>根據 base64 的編碼原理，尺寸比原文件要大，如果圖片稍微有點大，這個字符串會很長很長</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>圖片更新後，要清緩存的問題</td>\n<td>因為瀏覽器緩存是針對文件，所以只能緩存包含 base64 的文件，比如 HTML / CSS，這相比緩存圖片要弱的多</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 id=\"svg\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#svg\" aria-label=\"svg permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SVG</h4>\n<p>SVG 圖片 <a href=\"https://www.w3cplus.com/svg-tutorial?page=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">教程</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>矢量，放大不失真，可適配各種分辨率</li>\n<li>支持多色</li>\n<li>支持動畫</li>\n</ul>\n<img src=\"/traverse/8efd112550fae52b8d48caf3e54f0669/svg.gif\" alt=\"SVG\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;\">\n<p>SVG 壓縮 - <a href=\"https://jakearchibald.github.io/svgomg/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://jakearchibald.github.io/svgomg/</a></p>\n<h4 id=\"webp\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#webp\" aria-label=\"webp permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>WebP</h4>\n<p>WebP 是一種支持有損壓縮和無損壓縮的圖片文件格式，根據 Google 的測試，無損壓縮後的 WebP 比 PNG 文件少了26％的體積，有損壓縮後的 WebP圖片相比於等效質量指標的 JPEG 圖片減少了25％~34%的體積。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>無損壓縮：webp ≈ png * 26%</li>\n<li>有損壓縮：webp ≈ jpg * 25% ~ 34%</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"apng\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#apng\" aria-label=\"apng permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>APNG</h4>\n<p>基於 PNG 格式擴展的一種動畫格式，增加了對動畫圖像的支持，同時加入了 24 位元 圖像和 8 位元 Alpha 透明度的支持</p>\n<p>這意味著動畫將擁有更好的質量，其誕生的目的是為了替代老舊的 GIF 格式\n​\n使用 GIF 效果</p>\n<p><img src=\"/traverse/0e86a67ef578b9ed1c1be9a727ddeef4/loading.gif\" alt=\"loading\"></p>\n<p>使用 Apng 效果</p>\n<p><img src=\"/traverse/9feb9dd8763e03b3edbe42a6533710a7/loading-apng.gif\" alt=\"loading APNG\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"iconfont\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#iconfont\" aria-label=\"iconfont permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Iconfont</h4>\n<p>用字體庫當圖標庫</p>\n<h3 id=\"頁面布局\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%A0%81%E9%9D%A2%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80\" aria-label=\"頁面布局 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>頁面布局</h3>\n<h4 id=\"class命名\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#class%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D\" aria-label=\"class命名 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Class命名</h4>\n<p>頁面 - 模塊 - 元素，例：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.page-user .block-card .el-title</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> ... <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>可參考BEM、SMACSS…等命名方法</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"標籤語義化\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%A8%99%E7%B1%A4%E8%AA%9E%E7%BE%A9%E5%8C%96\" aria-label=\"標籤語義化 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>標籤語義化</h3>\n<p>語義標籤取代 Div</p>\n<p><img src=\"/traverse/02816b4ddef9cbfe98cf81188e63a054/html5-tags.gif\" alt=\"HTML5 tags\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"適配方案\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%81%A9%E9%85%8D%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\" aria-label=\"適配方案 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>適配方案</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; margin: initial;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64.44444444444444%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"responsive web design methodology\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/traverse/static/ba8dda81134188f3d2b950a51e9e66be/80e3c/rwd-method.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/traverse/static/ba8dda81134188f3d2b950a51e9e66be/4ec73/rwd-method.jpg 180w,\n/traverse/static/ba8dda81134188f3d2b950a51e9e66be/158ba/rwd-method.jpg 360w,\n/traverse/static/ba8dda81134188f3d2b950a51e9e66be/80e3c/rwd-method.jpg 720w,\n/traverse/static/ba8dda81134188f3d2b950a51e9e66be/fdf97/rwd-method.jpg 724w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>根據不同的需求，可以依照上面列出來的幾種方式去挑選合適的適配方案。\n值得一提的是Bootstrap是一套兼容PC至移動端響應式的套件，很適合拿來用在 缺少設計資源或後台管理網站\n另外，根據實際情況的不同頁面布局是可以混著用\n根據過往開發經驗，個人建議，大區塊用自適應，間距才用rem，因為rem換算出來有小數點，所以會有誤差</p>\n<h3 id=\"全屏適配\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%85%A8%E5%B1%8F%E9%81%A9%E9%85%8D\" aria-label=\"全屏適配 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>全屏適配</h3>\n<p>rem.js - 透過設備的分配率和DPI等參數，計算比例實踐全屏適配。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"成為大前端的起手式","date":"October 27, 2018","description":"簡單介紹如何從單純的JS開發者入門成為全方位的前端開發","tags":["front-end"],"donation":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/cross-platform-proxy-tool/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"跨平台 proxy 代理工具"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/all-resolutions-coverage-methodology/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"多端全螢幕適配方案"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"dc521a67-dae0-5f61-8b39-1b4b21090e3a","previousPostId":"4f056518-5b27-54d6-9da8-fa0cf91852e1","nextPostId":"e250a1c7-5c49-5687-a02b-fa1a8a439f66"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1824009237","2841359383"],"slicesMap":{}}